This product includes software developed by
Maryan Bogdanov as part of the Engineering Control Theory (ECT) project.

ECT-SDK is provided as a reference implementation of the
FXI–Δ–E deviation-based control architecture.

This software is distributed for verification, reproducibility,
and architectural evaluation purposes only.

The name "ECT", "ECT-SDK", and "Engineering Control Core"
are used to describe the original architecture and reference implementation
and do not imply endorsement of derivative works.

